704362f-a.title: Brooklyn: Flatlands Avenue - 107th Street (East)
704362f-a.text:
Flatlands Avenue, at East 107th Street, viewing north
toward Fresh Creek, where the W. P. A. is building a bridge
across the creek.
June 24, 1936
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
CSTT LNE IPERA I7E
